```plaintext

  Step 3: Move block with index 9 (yellow rectangular on the arches)
  Step 4: Move block with index 10 (half-cylinder on yellow rectangular)
  Step 5: Move block with index 1 (arch of right structure)
  Step 6: Move block with index 15 (left orange triangle)
  Step 7: Move block with index 15 (right orange triangle)
```
